 <span data-ttu-id="49518-149">참조 <xref:System.Xml.XmlUrlResolver.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 이 속성을 사용 하는 예입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="49518-149">See <xref:System.Xml.XmlUrlResolver.Credentials%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> for an example that uses this property.</span></span>
